OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Remaining dry this
OL,7,Fevening with variable amounts of cloud
OL,8,Fand some sunny intervals. Pleasantly
OL,9,Fwarm. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will remain dry with some
OL,14,Flengthy clear periods. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,17,Fwith some sunny spells, some cloud
OL,18,Fbubbling up by afternoon. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
